parameters: A Mimic pops out from the Chest!!!
\n<\N[4]>Just leave it to me, I'll get it.
\n<\N[3]>I'm sorry Cloudo, but your mum wouldn't like you climbing.
\n<\N[2]>Wait a tick, this has a different royal crest.
\n<\N[2]>The one is very different, but it says.
\n<\N[2]>"\C[17]Caeruleum crystals\C[0] will be the way forward, it shall protect us from all evils."
\n<\N[2]>"Our land was not blessed with the gift of fire and warmth, however our technology has given us great protection."
\n<\N[2]>"We must head westward to fulfill our destiny, and save those brutes from their own destruction."
\n<\N[2]>"The power of ice is a mighty force, it protects us with this mighty shield we call home."
\n<\N[2]>"Our leader is wise and true, he will make a great sacrifice to guarantee our victory in the next battle."
